---
---
<section class="latest-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="latest-eyebrow">
      <span class="latest-line"></span>
      <span class="latest-label">Latest</span>
    </div>
    <a href="/research/q1-2026-banking-earnings/" class="latest-card">
      <div class="latest-card-top">
        <div class="latest-meta">
          <span class="latest-category">Research</span>
          <span class="latest-sep">·</span>
          <span class="latest-date">April 2026</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="latest-title">Q1 2026 Banking Earnings: What the Numbers Are Really Saying</h2>
        <p class="latest-excerpt">JPMorgan set the tone. Wells Fargo is still transitioning. Capital One completed the Discover acquisition. Ally is the one to watch — and hasn't reported yet.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="latest-card-bottom">
        <div class="latest-tags">
          <span class="tag">Banking</span>
          <span class="tag">Earnings</span>
          <span class="tag">Q1 2026</span>
        </div>
        <span class="latest-read">Read <span class="latest-arrow">→</span></span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  .latest-section { border-top:1px solid var(--rule); padding-block:64px; }
  .latest-eyebrow { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:24px; }
  .latest-line { display:block; width:24px; height:1px; background:var(--accent); flex-shrink:0; }
  .latest-label { font-family:var(--font-body); font-size:11px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-muted); }
  .latest-card { display:block; border:0.5px solid var(--rule); padding:32px 36px; border-radius:2px; transition:border-color 0.2s; }
  .latest-card:hover { border-color:var(--accent); }
  .latest-card:hover .latest-arrow { transform:translateX(4px); }
  .latest-meta { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .latest-category { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--accent); font-weight:500; }
  .latest-sep { color:var(--ink-faint); font-size:11px; }
  .latest-date { font-size:11px; color:var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing:0.06em; }
  .latest-title { font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:clamp(20px,2.4vw,32px); font-weight:400; color:var(--ink); line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .latest-excerpt { font-size:14px; line-height:1.8; color:var(--ink-muted); font-weight:300; margin-bottom:24px; }
  .latest-card-bottom { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:16px; }
  .latest-tags { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; }
  .tag { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-muted); border:1px solid var(--rule); padding:4px 10px; border-radius:2px; }
  .latest-read { font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-muted); display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; white-space:nowrap; flex-shrink:0; }
  .latest-arrow { display:inline-block; transition:transform 0.25s; }
  @media (max-width:640px) {
    .latest-card { padding:20px 22px; }
    .latest-card-bottom { flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-start; gap:12px; }
  }
</style>
